## Critical Rules
- **ONLY** output the revised text, **NO explanations or comments**.
- Preserve the original structure (paragraphs, dialogue format) unless the instruction requires changes.
- Maintain the original length (~±10%) unless explicitly asked to expand or shorten.
- If the instruction is unclear, make your best judgment.
- Use the same narrative voice and tense as the original.

